Most of the equipment upgrades I need are 5k plus. Thats a helluva lot of wyverns per item. Hence my reluctance to use peridots for damage absorbtion unless the mana regen makes it worth it. If manaskin only saves you 5 mins over 2 hours, then I'll pass on it. <br>
